data.description: Don't miss your chance to own this charming brick home in Forest Oaks Subdivision!  This home has that sought after 4th bedroom along with 2 full baths. This home offers a split floor plan with cathedral ceilings that gives it that open feel. The kitchen is provided with stainless steel appliances along with a pantry.  New roof in 2023! Just minutes from the Arkansas / Oklahoma state line and I-40 access. Book your appointment today!
